    ☐ Support for gRPC log target.
    ☐ Support for syslog log target.
    ☐ Support for structured log target.
    ☐ Support for SQL database log target.
    ☐ Support for InfluxDB database log target.
    ☐ Support for MongoDB database log target.
  Managed Object Management:

  Platform Abstraction Layer:
    ☐ Basic gRPC support.
    ☐ Basic SQL database support.
    ☐ Basic Redis support.
    ☐ Basic InfluxDB support.
    ☐ Basic MongoDB support.
    ☐ Basic JIRA support.
    ☐ Add support for network objects as VFS resources.
    ☐ Add support for database objects as VFS resources.
  Password Management:

  Service:

  Utilities:

